WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.448
We did it, family.

00:00:01.448 --> 00:00:08.754
We stopped him—the man I told you I saw in the spirit who was going to try to do something at Trump's rally.

00:00:08.754 --> 00:00:16.650
There were two different articles sent to me by two different viewers telling me, "Hey Brandon, look what happened at Coachella.

00:00:16.650 --> 00:00:25.679
" I told everybody we must pray for Coachella because there's an attempt on Trump that was going to be there, and I told everybody, "Hey, they're going to try to shoot people in the crowd.

00:00:25.679 --> 00:00:29.942
This is going to be a big deal; we have to pray against this.

00:00:29.942 --> 00:00:37.160
" Well, nothing was said all day yesterday about any kind of anything in the news.

00:00:37.160 --> 00:00:43.360
Well, today I'm getting all these articles from people telling me, "Brandon, look, he was stopped.

00:00:43.740 --> 00:00:54.404
" He had a fake security pass, a fake press pass; he had all kinds of things to try to get inside the event to try to get close to Trump.

00:00:54.404 --> 00:01:06.600
So I just want to give all the glory to God, for He shows the watchman on the wall to warn them to pray on behalf of whatever He needs them to be praying for.

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:11.560
We are making a difference, and I just want to encourage you all.

00:01:11.560 --> 00:01:18.742
Thank you for coming and praying with me and my little prayer group here.

00:01:18.742 --> 00:01:22.428
I am so excited, I'm speechless.

00:01:22.428 --> 00:01:24.309
I'm just like, "Wow, thank you, Lord.

00:01:24.309 --> 00:01:25.651
Look at what we're doing.

00:01:25.651 --> 00:01:28.840
" We're making a difference, and I just want to encourage you to keep going.

00:01:28.840 --> 00:01:33.940
We have to pray; there are still things we have to pray about clear up until after the election.

00:01:33.940 --> 00:01:36.496
So we're going to be making these prayer videos.

00:01:36.742 --> 00:01:38.559
Here's our prayer video today.

00:01:38.559 --> 00:01:41.150
So God bless you all and thank you.

00:01:41.150 --> 00:01:48.171
And then they had the big prayer thing in Washington, D.

00:01:48.171 --> 00:01:49.183
C.

00:02:00.709 --> 00:02:01.329
, and nothing happened there.

00:02:01.329 --> 00:02:03.800
We interceded for that.

00:02:15.520 --> 00:02:19.235
I was praying for protection over the people, that no secret enemy attacks or anything would happen during the big prayer thing with Jonathan Cahn.

00:02:19.235 --> 00:02:29.880
From what I saw, nothing evil happened at all there, and there were probably 20,000 to 30,000 people there.

00:02:30.330 --> 00:02:48.159
It was a lot of people in the camera shot who were interceding, taking communion, and praying for this nation, and they were worshiping Jesus.

00:02:48.159 --> 00:02:52.604
You could feel the presence of the Lord tangibly when I was watching it.

00:02:52.604 --> 00:02:59.450
If you didn't watch that, go back and watch that again.

00:03:01.510 --> 00:03:09.719
I believe they probably have a replay on Jonathan Cahn's YouTube channel.

00:03:09.719 --> 00:03:18.411
So I encourage everybody to watch that; that was a real blessing.

00:03:18.411 --> 00:03:26.400
It blessed me; I could feel the presence of the Lord.

00:03:26.400 --> 00:03:46.683
It made me want to weep because people were crying out for repentance, seeking the Lord, and this is what it's going to take for revival.

00:03:46.683 --> 00:04:12.212
If my people, who are called by my name, will humble themselves and pray and turn from their wicked ways, He said we would hear from heaven and He would heal our land.

00:04:25.240 --> 00:04:33.760
I believe that God is not done with America yet, that there is one last revival that will take place.

00:04:33.760 --> 00:04:49.055
He said, "Brandon, there will be a shaking to awaken," and whatever it takes, His remnant right now is preparing themselves.

00:04:49.055 --> 00:05:00.820
We're ready, and we're getting our hearts ready before Him right now as the glorious church ready for a great revival.

00:05:08.177 --> 00:05:14.440
I believe with all my heart we're about to see the demonstrations and manifestations of the glory of God like we've never seen before.

00:05:14.440 --> 00:05:27.440
Like He said to me, "Brandon, the old wells are becoming uncapped, and we're going to go down to the deep parts.

00:05:27.440 --> 00:05:37.960
" People say, "Well, we want to go back and just see those old revivals.

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:52.080
" No, I want something new, something fresh—a new, fresh experience of the presence of the Lord, not the old thing.

00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:54.840
Let's do something new.

00:05:59.461 --> 00:06:04.033
So I'm excited for what the Lord is about to do.

00:06:09.560 --> 00:06:34.680
The old revivals, the old Harbinger Church, the old tent revivals, the old outpouring like it was at Azusa—I believe that we'll see something greater: the former and latter rain together in a greater way in these last seconds of these last hours.

00:06:39.464 --> 00:06:43.030
This is a pillow my wife put on there so you all could see it.

00:06:43.490 --> 00:06:55.968
I got this at Nancy DeFrain's healing thing she did at the church, and this is Jesus the Healer.

00:06:55.968 --> 00:07:07.994
What a witness and a testimony of who Jesus is and what He does for the body of Christ to wear.

00:07:07.994 --> 00:07:31.773
You could probably get that on her ministry website, Nancy DeFrain Ministries, but she has these "Jesus the Healer" sweatshirts, and I thought that was so cool, so I got me one.

00:07:31.773 --> 00:07:42.180
But my wife put it on a pillow so you all could see it.

00:07:42.180 --> 00:07:49.349
It has an eagle on the front, too.

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:55.359
I thought that was pretty cool.

00:07:55.359 --> 00:08:04.599
I just love the witness of it because it's who I am.

00:08:04.599 --> 00:08:16.687
I believe it with all my heart that Jesus is a healer, and so I said, "That's perfect, I'll wear it.

00:08:16.687 --> 00:08:23.300
" I was excited she got that for me.

00:08:23.300 --> 00:08:34.240
So I just want to encourage you all today about the visitations and the manifestations of angelic encounters.

00:08:37.742 --> 00:09:00.600
I believe what the Lord showed me—He said, "As you're getting closer and closer," and this was several years ago He told me this—He said, "You're going to start to experience more angelic visitations than you've ever experienced before, Brandon.

00:09:00.600 --> 00:09:03.560
" And it has been so.

00:09:03.560 --> 00:09:13.959
I've had a lot of encounters from angelic help and divine protection.

00:09:13.959 --> 00:09:18.009
I've seen secret service angels.

00:09:26.970 --> 00:09:28.200
The Lord shows me these things, and I'm excited about it.

00:09:32.200 --> 00:09:39.320
But He told me, "I want you to go on and encourage my people today about expecting divine protection, expecting divine whatever.

00:09:41.897 --> 00:09:44.279
" I mean, whatever you need, the Lord has it.

00:10:06.824 --> 00:10:07.079
I believe with all my heart we're in a time like never before.

00:10:07.079 --> 00:10:13.240
We're going to see things like we've never seen before.

00:10:13.240 --> 00:10:36.080
I'll tell you some of the visitations that I've had on this for just a second—I'll give you one or two of them and then we'll pray—but I just want to encourage you.

00:10:36.080 --> 00:10:40.020
Let's take communion together again.

00:10:40.020 --> 00:10:52.720
I've got my communion, and I just wanted to lift it up before the Lord.

00:10:52.720 --> 00:11:01.531
Today is Yom Kippur, so it's a day of atonement.

00:11:02.988 --> 00:11:13.840
I know it's probably already over for some of you, but I'm going to act like it's happening right now.

00:11:13.840 --> 00:11:31.995
Yom Kippur is happening right now, and we're going to take communion just like they did in Washington, D.

00:11:31.995 --> 00:11:32.940
C.

00:11:32.940 --> 00:11:39.964
, together as believers lifting up America, Australia, Asia, Europe, and Africa.

00:11:39.964 --> 00:11:45.773
We're lifting up our nations before the Lord.

00:11:45.773 --> 00:12:02.520
If we humble ourselves and pray—He didn't say if the world does this, He said, "If My people do it"—that's us.

00:12:02.520 --> 00:12:05.526
We're His children.

00:12:05.526 --> 00:12:52.023
He said if you humble yourself and pray and turn from your wicked ways, I believe, Lord, that we turn from our wicked ways and that we'll have one last revival, one last major push, a harvest of souls like we've never seen before.

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:06.639
I saw great things coming for demonstrations and manifestations: arms growing out, eyes coming back.

00:13:06.639 --> 00:13:15.169
I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, walking in the supernatural will be like taking a breath, just like stepping over.

00:13:15.169 --> 00:13:36.400
A lot of times we pray and pray to get over there, but the more you get closer to praying, you'll understand what I'm talking about.

00:13:36.400 --> 00:13:53.799
Praying and interceding sometimes takes time to get over that river, but the Lord said it would be as close as stepping over into those rivers, those geysers, is what I want to call them—to step over and feel that.

00:14:13.090 --> 00:14:13.520
He said it would be like taking a breath; it will be effortless, sweatless victories.

00:14:13.520 --> 00:14:40.626
That's a good word: sweatless victories where you just step into the supernatural and you get your manifestation of what you're believing for like a light switch.

00:14:40.626 --> 00:14:47.920
He said it would be like flipping on a light switch.

00:14:47.920 --> 00:15:12.744
It's not going to be hard where you intercede for hours to see a turn in the spirit realm; He said it's like taking a breath, you just step over.

00:15:12.744 --> 00:15:14.759
Glory to God!

00:15:14.759 --> 00:15:29.150
For somebody who prays like I do, that is awesome.

00:15:29.150 --> 00:15:30.369
It's exciting.

00:15:42.724 --> 00:15:42.929
I just go, "Oh, thank you, Lord.

00:15:42.929 --> 00:16:01.227
" But it's not something far off; I believe it's today as we're entering into this Yom Kippur, the Day of Atonement.

00:16:01.227 --> 00:16:09.963
Rosh Hashanah is over and we've entered into that holy time.

00:16:21.360 --> 00:16:25.240
I believe we're in a time right now—first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation.

00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:49.359
I don't want to take your time just jabbering, so let's take this communion today and let's enter into His throne room boldly as His kids, not as orphans or strangers, but friends of the King today.

00:16:51.919 --> 00:16:59.160
I want you all to be bold about it, saying, "Dad, I'm home.

00:17:17.422 --> 00:17:19.048
I'm here with You.

00:17:19.048 --> 00:17:24.853
I'm sitting on Your throne.

00:17:24.853 --> 00:17:29.799
I'm seated with You in the heavenlies.

00:17:29.799 --> 00:17:38.252
You dwell in me, and as I breathe, You breathe with me.

00:17:38.252 --> 00:17:40.112
We're one.

00:17:41.960 --> 00:17:45.440
The Holy Spirit and I are one.

00:17:48.742 --> 00:17:56.546
" So Father, we just lift up this body before You, and we thank You for the Day of Atonement.

00:17:56.546 --> 00:18:10.100
We thank You, Lord, that You've washed us in Your blood, that You have atoned for all our sins.

00:18:10.100 --> 00:18:23.191
You took all our disease, our mental anguish, our suffering, mental torments, depressions, anxieties, and fears.

00:18:23.191 --> 00:18:36.498
Jesus, You paid the price, and it's by Your covenant—by the body that was broken for us.

00:18:36.498 --> 00:18:42.510
I thank You, Father, that You are our healer.

00:18:42.510 --> 00:18:51.351
According to Your word, Lord, You said, "By My stripes, you are healed.

00:18:51.351 --> 00:19:06.657
" As I take this body, Lord, I thank You that You dwell in me, and there's no place for sickness and disease in my body—no virus.

00:19:06.657 --> 00:19:25.480
We're going into the winter months, Lord, and I thank You that You are my flu shot, You are my C-word shot; You have it all.

00:19:25.680 --> 00:19:38.106
You cover us, and I believe that You are my protector, that no weapon, no pestilence, no plague comes nigh me.

00:19:39.415 --> 00:19:52.611
I take this, Father, and I thank You, Lord; this is my Holy Ghost vaccination.

00:19:52.611 --> 00:19:56.255
Lord, I thank You for Your protection over me.

00:20:09.710 --> 00:20:10.140
You have been good, and Your mercy is new every morning; Your mercy endures forever.

00:20:10.140 --> 00:20:13.040
Thank You, Father.

00:20:13.040 --> 00:20:17.970
Now, Lord, we take the blood.

00:20:17.970 --> 00:20:32.400
We thank You for Your blood, Lord, that all our sins are washed away.

00:20:50.217 --> 00:20:50.589
It is by the blood of the Lamb and by the word of our testimony.

00:20:50.589 --> 00:20:54.444
It's a holy thing.

00:20:54.444 --> 00:21:05.295
We don't flippantly do it, but we do it with all our heart.

00:21:05.295 --> 00:21:18.434
Jesus' blood was shed for me, it was shed for them, and I thank You for Your blood.

00:21:25.620 --> 00:21:26.130
I thank You for the cross.

00:21:41.568 --> 00:21:41.857
I thank You for washing over me.

00:21:43.013 --> 00:21:52.200
The blood of Jesus washes me, and You watch over me, my children, and my wife.

00:21:52.200 --> 00:21:57.672
Father, I thank You for the protection of Your blood.

00:21:57.672 --> 00:22:06.839
We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

00:22:16.286 --> 00:22:16.893
We take this blood right now in the name of Jesus.

00:22:16.893 --> 00:22:28.040
Thank You, Lord, that You atoned for our sins; You don't even remember them.

00:22:28.040 --> 00:22:47.200
Thank You, Lord, for Your mercy, for healing us by the covenant You gave to us.

00:22:47.200 --> 00:23:04.963
Greater works will we do because You went to the Father and sent us the Comforter, the Holy Spirit, who dwells on the inside of us.

00:23:04.963 --> 00:23:09.360
Holy Spirit, we invite You into this time.

00:23:09.360 --> 00:23:28.089
Thank You for this day, for this is the day the Lord has made and we will rejoice and be glad in it.

00:23:28.089 --> 00:23:38.000
We want You to be our friend, our standby, our helper.

00:23:38.444 --> 00:23:45.440
You said You would teach us and guide us into all things.

00:23:45.440 --> 00:23:52.297
Whatever it is, You have the answer.

00:23:52.297 --> 00:24:12.799
We do not lean on our own intellect—because that would be really bad for me—but Lord, I thank You that we have the mind of Christ.

00:24:19.549 --> 00:24:42.384
I thank You that You're the captain, and I'm not even the co-captain, Lord; I just sit in the back and let You steer the ship in every area of my life.

00:24:42.384 --> 00:24:59.736
Father, I thank You that You have a perfect plan for us—perfect peace, perfect everything—because we're allowing You to steer our lives.

00:25:14.382 --> 00:25:20.942
You said, "Trust in the Lord with all your heart, and lean not unto your own understanding, but in all your ways acknowledge Him, and He shall direct your paths.

00:25:29.049 --> 00:25:32.582
" We trust You, Lord.

00:25:41.742 --> 00:25:42.031
We let go.

00:25:42.031 --> 00:25:52.549
It may not make any sense at all, but it doesn't have to when you're trusting Jesus.

00:25:52.549 --> 00:26:00.900
We reach forth and grab onto the new thing, letting go of the past.

00:26:11.316 --> 00:26:12.493
I'm not going to keep looking back over my shoulder; I press on for You, Jesus, and look for the fresh things.

00:26:12.493 --> 00:26:15.180
God has our future.

00:26:15.180 --> 00:26:26.874
"Beloved, I wish above all things that thou mayest prosper and be in health, even as thy soul prospers.

00:26:26.874 --> 00:26:38.969
" So I'm going to talk to you all about angelic visitations.

00:26:38.969 --> 00:26:57.973
One night, my wife and I were lying in bed asleep, probably about 4:00 in the morning, and all of a sudden we felt our whole roof shake.

00:26:59.725 --> 00:27:02.399
I thought somebody was breaking in.

00:27:06.770 --> 00:27:11.457
It was so strong that it literally felt like something was coming through.

00:27:24.640 --> 00:27:24.831
It woke us both up.

00:27:36.480 --> 00:27:47.631
I flew out of bed, turned on the light, grabbed my firearm, and was going toward the door when instantaneously my eyes were translated over to the realm of the spirit.

00:27:55.039 --> 00:28:00.706
The Lord allowed me to see these three massive pig-looking demons with long evil noses and eyes that were red and slanted.

00:28:00.706 --> 00:28:05.914
They had scaly skin and long nasty hair—of course, it's a demon.

00:28:05.914 --> 00:28:17.040
One was like a black mist or a fog that you could see through, but it had evil red eyes.

00:28:19.279 --> 00:28:29.440
The other one looked like a pig, and the third one was red and very gnarly-looking with big black horns.

00:28:29.440 --> 00:28:34.617
It looked like something off of A Witch's Invitation with Carman.

00:28:36.396 --> 00:28:42.120
They were hissing and growling, but they couldn't get close to the house.

00:28:42.120 --> 00:28:46.399
It's like they were being blocked.

00:28:48.839 --> 00:28:59.672
I know I put a bloodline around my home, but at this time I was just staring at them.

00:29:02.840 --> 00:29:18.011
It was like when you see a bull scrape the dirt; they were scraping the dirt like they were trying to get traction to come at me, but they couldn't.

00:29:18.011 --> 00:29:23.930
All of a sudden, I see these massive angelic beings.

00:29:29.480 --> 00:29:36.419
They were massive, and they had their arms interlocked—they had their hands on their hips and were locked together.

00:29:36.419 --> 00:29:39.359
I believe there were three or four of them.

00:29:46.239 --> 00:29:52.028
They were standing up, and I bet they were seventeen feet high—massive, bigger than my tree out front—and they were wide.

00:29:52.028 --> 00:29:55.030
They were glowing with glory.

00:29:55.030 --> 00:30:06.879
When I looked over and saw them protecting me, they didn't have swords or shields; they were just a wall.

00:30:06.879 --> 00:30:16.905
They had these beautiful gowns on, and their voices were like thunder when they spoke.

00:30:31.255 --> 00:30:31.483
It sounded like a thunderous echo.

00:30:31.483 --> 00:30:36.919
When I saw them standing there, I said, "Praise the Lord!

00:30:43.423 --> 00:30:46.824
" And when I said that, they turned back and looked at me and said, "Praise the Lord!

00:31:00.428 --> 00:31:00.993
" They started worshiping the Lord with me.

00:31:00.993 --> 00:31:11.480
Every single time they said "Praise the Lord," it echoed throughout the neighborhood.

00:31:11.480 --> 00:31:19.690
It wasn't in the natural; it was the spirit.

00:31:23.571 --> 00:31:29.559
I want to tell you all: the spirit realm is more real than the natural realm.

00:31:29.559 --> 00:31:34.731
It's just one breath away.

00:31:52.528 --> 00:31:52.852
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

00:31:52.852 --> 00:32:03.627
Instantaneously, we go into the spirit realm, and the angels were crying, "Praise the Lord!

00:32:03.627 --> 00:32:22.915
" At this time, I see a portal open over to the east, and I can see into the glory, into the heavens.

00:32:22.915 --> 00:32:33.720
There was light up there, and you could see the holy city.

00:32:46.519 --> 00:32:56.573
All of a sudden, when they said "Praise the Lord," that light from heaven—the glory—shined down on those angels and made them glow.

00:32:57.811 --> 00:33:04.149
They started glowing with the glory, and their faces shined.

00:33:04.149 --> 00:33:08.549
I said, "Holy, holy, holy is the Lord!

00:33:09.429 --> 00:33:14.873
" and they said, "Holy, holy, holy is the Lord!

00:33:15.576 --> 00:33:18.600
" You could hear it through the atmosphere.

00:33:22.926 --> 00:33:24.724
I stood there and watched this for a long time because it was beautiful.

00:33:24.724 --> 00:33:36.063
As I was worshiping, they worshiped with me, and I didn't even pay attention to the devils anymore.

00:33:49.085 --> 00:33:49.500
They went away as we worshiped.

00:33:56.889 --> 00:34:01.419
I was so fixed on those angelic beings that I had completely forgotten the devils were there.

00:34:01.419 --> 00:34:11.359
When I looked back down, they were gone.

00:34:11.719 --> 00:34:15.609
I guess they got scared away.

00:34:22.359 --> 00:34:22.926
But I want to tell you, your angels keep charge over you.

00:34:22.926 --> 00:34:35.179
Psalm 91 says they would bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:34:35.179 --> 00:34:41.599
I believe with all my heart that's happening all the time and we don't even know it.

00:34:41.599 --> 00:34:46.945
Well, I went to work the next day at the church.

00:34:49.733 --> 00:34:53.428
I was so excited because we had a staff meeting.

00:34:53.428 --> 00:35:02.140
I told the pastor the whole thing, and he said, "Brandon, I don't doubt it.

00:35:02.140 --> 00:35:08.435
I actually see a glow on your face.

00:35:15.919 --> 00:35:16.259
" The holy glow was still shining on me.

00:35:17.369 --> 00:35:28.667
He said he could see a tangible manifestation of the spirit of the Lord on my face.

00:35:39.897 --> 00:35:40.446
That visitation changed my life.

00:35:40.446 --> 00:35:50.520
I learned how to deal with stuff in the spirit realm more and more.

00:36:01.040 --> 00:36:01.354
It's like trial and error—one day at a time.

00:36:01.354 --> 00:36:04.754
Nobody really ever mentored me.

00:36:04.754 --> 00:36:19.794
I used to think you had to be friends with upper leadership or rub shoulders with them to get your call.

00:36:24.800 --> 00:36:37.000
You go to conferences and want to sit on the front row so they'll notice you and give you a prophecy.

00:36:42.968 --> 00:36:50.769
I realized I went to all the revivals and worked for mega-churches, putting myself in a position to be seen because I knew God had a call on me.

00:36:52.541 --> 00:37:00.130
I wanted any guest speaker or prophet to see me on the front row.

00:37:00.130 --> 00:37:04.166
How many times did I wait in the back room just to say hi to the pastor?

00:37:04.166 --> 00:37:13.460
But the more I pushed for it, the more they looked at me and said, "We don't see it.

00:37:16.090 --> 00:37:16.720
In fact, we see you're a janitor.

00:37:18.520 --> 00:37:18.760
" And I kept cleaning.

00:37:19.480 --> 00:37:34.928
I had certain dear people who would see it, and big ministers who laid hands on me, but I'd always come back and quote them: "So-and-so said this about me.

00:37:44.307 --> 00:37:44.520
" It gave me just enough encouragement to keep going.

00:37:45.631 --> 00:37:58.160
But you don't need to rub shoulders with your pastor for your call to come to pass.

00:37:58.160 --> 00:38:03.169
Now I sit in the back row a lot.

00:38:03.169 --> 00:38:24.340
I don't need them to tip their hat toward me; Jesus tipped His hat toward me and said, "Start a YouTube channel.

00:38:24.340 --> 00:38:32.582
" What He's done has been amazing, and nobody else can take the glory for it.

